title: Tyga shows love for Kylie by kissing her onstage
text:
0 0 0 0 0 
Washington D.C., Oct . 6(ANI): Seems like Tyga just took his love for Kylie Jenner to another level as he recently pulled up his girlfriend to show some PDA during his performance. 
According to a fan video, the rapper pulled up the 18-year-old reality star on stage while he was performing ‘Stimulated,’ reports E! Online. 
Jenner, who donned an all blue Adidas track suit and white tennis shoes, hugged and kissed her boyfriend as he continued to rap the song he wrote about her. (ANI) Related Posts
